@UserManagementAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5011

### 测试API根路径 - 应该显示Swagger UI
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/

###

### 获取所有用户
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### 获取特定用户 (ID: 1)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 获取不存在的用户 (ID: 999)
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/999
Accept: application/json

###

### 创建新用户
POST {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "David Wilson",
  "email": "david@techhive.com"
}

###

### 创建用户 - 邮箱已存在（应该返回409冲突）
POST {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Another Alice",
  "email": "alice@techhive.com"
}

###

### 创建用户 - 无效数据（应该返回400错误）
POST {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "A",
  "email": "invalid-email"
}

###

### 更新用户 (ID: 1)
PUT {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Smith Updated",
  "email": "alice.smith.updated@techhive.com",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 更新不存在的用户 (ID: 999)
PUT {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Non Existent User",
  "email": "nonexistent@techhive.com",
  "isActive": true
}

###

### 获取活跃用户
GET {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/active
Accept: application/json

###

### 删除用户 (ID: 3)
DELETE {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/3

###

### 删除不存在的用户 (ID: 999)
DELETE {{UserManagementAPI_HostAddress}}/api/users/999

###
